item.description: (via Bristol's Blog) Mr. President, When Should I Expect Your Call?: Dear President Obama, You do... http://t.co/oIXONnSk @sarahpalinusa
item.content:encoded: (via Bristol's Blog) Mr. President, When Should I Expect Your Call?: Dear President Obama, You do... http://t.co/oIXONnSk @sarahpalinusa You don’t know my telephone number, but I hope your staff is busy trying to find it. Ever since you called Sandra Fluke after Rush Limbaugh called her a slut, I figured I might be next. You explained to reporters you called her because you were thinking of your two daughters, Malia and Sasha. After all, you didn’t want them to think it was okay for men to treat them that way: Link - Trackbacks
